trans-unit.source: The IAccIdentity and all of its exposed members are part of a managed wrapper for the Component Object Model (COM) <xref uid="langword_csharp_IAccIdentity" name="IAccIdentity" href=""></xref> interface.

trans-unit.source: Specifies which child of the IAccessible object the caller wants to identify.
trans-unit.target: 指定子 Cwnd 物件的呼叫端想要識別。

trans-unit.source: Address of a variable that receives a pointer to a callee-allocated identity string.
trans-unit.target: 此變數會接收被呼叫端配置的識別字串的指標位址。

trans-unit.source: The callee allocates the identity string using <xref uid="langword_csharp_CoTaskMemAlloc" name="CoTaskMemAlloc" href=""></xref>; the caller must release the identity string by using <xref uid="langword_csharp_CoTaskMemFree" name="CoTaskMemFree" href=""></xref> when finished.
trans-unit.target: 被呼叫端配置的識別字串使用<xref uid="langword_csharp_CoTaskMemAlloc" name="CoTaskMemAlloc" href=""> </xref>; 呼叫端必須使用發行的識別字串<xref uid="langword_csharp_CoTaskMemFree" name="CoTaskMemFree" href=""></xref>時完成。

trans-unit.source: Address of a variable that receives the length, in bytes, of the callee-allocated identity string.
trans-unit.target: 此變數會接收長度，以位元組為單位被呼叫端配置的識別字串的位址。
